name: id
doc: Get the model number and firmware version.

name: blade_type
doc: Get/Set the blade type (for set n is number indicated in section 6.4).

name: reg_in_freq
doc: Get the current supplied external reference frequency.

name: harmonic_mul
doc: Get/Set Harmonic Multiplier applied to external reference frequency (1-15).

name: harmonic_divider
doc:
Get/Set the Harmonic Divider applied to external reference frequency (1-
15).

name: verbose
doc:
Get/Set verbose mode is set to 1, status messages are output on the 
USB
